<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3149178" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="CHG" oldref="65">In spreadsheets and documents in which form controls are used, you can click the <emph>Find Record</emph> icon on the form bar to open a dialog to find any text and values. </paragraph>
</tablecell>
